    General Stores in Dahisar, Mumbai

    General stores or mom-n-pop shops are known as 'kiranas' in most parts of the country. There's bound to be a general shop located at every other corner of any neighbourhood. Now with the emergence of the various forms of modern retail, many of these establishments are evolving from its traditional format to a more modern, department store format. Any of these stores house a vast variety of products ranging from loose grains and pulses to cosmetics. A modern general store may have air-conditioning, a wider range of products and services that local shops may not offer. Following the traditional system, most serve customers through a counter system, certain stores encourage self-service for their customers, by following a more modern system. Certain retail stores have set up their own online store enabling a customer to purchase groceries and other essential products online and have it delivered to the desired address. You can find one from a large number of General Stores in Dahisar, Mumbai from the list given above.
